transcript_chunks.text: here we are born to be kings, Craig's the princes of the universe, Greg is a mortal, he has inside him blood of kings. Sometimes I don't know who's more annoying. You heard the dog. It's the dog for sure. You love him. I love him, but he's a nightmare sometimes. Look at him.
